  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764970/extras/86ecd83bd5e9e71bfca7a86fb365a65e.avif?t=1726618264\" width=622 height=145 /></span><br>A contemplative, single-player 2D navigation game with easy controls, yet challenging.<br><br>Move: A W S D or ← ↑ ↓ →<br>Action: Space<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Original soundtrack and neat sound design to create an immersive and thrilling experience. <br></li><li>There are several obstacles in the game, but the \"checkpoints\" make the experience less punitive. <br></li><li>During gameplay there are no texts, and no need for them.<br></li><li>Animations, symbols and mechanics communicate to the player everything necessary to enjoy the experience.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764970/extras/49824b9ebfbd12467a46c504977e6eee.avif?t=1726618264\" width=622 height=272 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764970/extras/be99776b429f69f3ddcc405d8472ac46.webp?t=1726618264\" width=16 height=18 /></span> A dark and hostile world. There are many traps in this place.<br>Can you continue? Can you find it?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764970/extras/26f56f65357d2171522b5b3038cbf9c5.webp?t=1726618264\" width=21 height=20 /></span>Navigate cautiously. Take it easy. Pay attention to the clues. And everything will be fine.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764970/extras/9638094d95d05e187f8e858ff66fca63.avif?t=1726618264\" width=622 height=95 /></span><br>With an enigmatic atmosphere, sometimes even dark, and beautiful scenery, \"Echo - An Indie Tale\" will conquer you.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764970/extras/86ecd83bd5e9e71bfca7a86fb365a65e.avif?t=1726618264\" width=622 height=145 /></span><br>A contemplative, single-player 2D navigation game with easy controls, yet challenging.<br><br>Move: A W S D or ← ↑ ↓ →<br>Action: Space<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Original soundtrack and neat sound design to create an immersive and thrilling experience. <br></li><li>There are several obstacles in the game, but the \"checkpoints\" make the experience less punitive. <br></li><li>During gameplay there are no texts, and no need for them.<br></li><li>Animations, symbols and mechanics communicate to the player everything necessary to enjoy the experience.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764970/extras/49824b9ebfbd12467a46c504977e6eee.avif?t=1726618264\" width=622 height=272 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764970/extras/be99776b429f69f3ddcc405d8472ac46.webp?t=1726618264\" width=16 height=18 /></span> A dark and hostile world. There are many traps in this place.<br>Can you continue? Can you find it?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764970/extras/26f56f65357d2171522b5b3038cbf9c5.webp?t=1726618264\" width=21 height=20 /></span>Navigate cautiously. Take it easy. Pay attention to the clues. And everything will be fine.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764970/extras/9638094d95d05e187f8e858ff66fca63.avif?t=1726618264\" width=622 height=95 /></span><br>With an enigmatic atmosphere, sometimes even dark, and beautiful scenery, \"Echo - An Indie Tale\" will conquer you.",
